title: The Dax Riggs Collection part 5 (Dax Riggs & T-daks) Final
description:
This torrent contains Unreleased, albums, demos and live recordings of Dax Riggs during his past and current solo projects.

Dax Riggs (born 15 October 1973 in Evansville, Indiana, United States), is a musician from Houma, Louisiana often remembered for fronting the sludge band Acid Bath in the 1990s. Dax has been a part of many projects since then, including Agents of Oblivion and Deadboy & the Elephantmen. In 2007 he began releasing material under his own name. He currently resides in Austin, Texas.
